PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of TIMOTHY REID, of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Jeffery Lyons, whose term has expired.
